description: Erection of 43 storey (147 metres) building with retail, restaurant with takeaway use (Use Class A1/A3/A5) on the ground and 1st floors and 399 residential units above, and a four storey (17 metres) pavilion building with retail, restaurant or takeaway use (Use Class A1/A3/A5) on the ground floor and 9 residential units above, landscaping and public open space, with parking and servicing facilities to the rear and at basement level.
